name: CHANEL
description: Fashion designer Coco Chanel is famous for her timeless designs, trademark suits and little black dresses.

name: DIOR
description: Dior, a brand rooted in history and just as luxurious as it sounds. An internationally renowned brand since 1946, the French fashion house acclaimed for its elegance and timeless femininity.

name: Tom Ford
description: Tom Ford clothes are known as elegant, classy, and glamorous. Stunning menswear, beautiful fragrances, top-quality sunglasses, impressive watches are just some of the Tom Ford clothes, very popular among high fashion lovers.

name: Kayali
description: In 2019 Huda and Mona Kattan launched Kayali a luxury fragrance brand that is available at The Beauty Editor in-store and online! Kayali means  in Arabic and the fragrances are the brainchild of both Huda and her sister Mona.

name: DAISY
description: Distinguishing characteristics of the flowers called daisy include a central, buttonlike disk of microscopic flowers encompassed by a ring of raylike petals. The similarities end here. The central disk can be flat, concave, or convex in form.

name: Byredo
description: Byredo fragrance there is. It's easy to see why the Stockholm-based brand is so popular. In addition to the incredibly chic and minimal packaging, the unisex scents are as unique as they come yet undoubtedly wearable and intriguing as well.

name: My way
description: This feminine fragrance combines consciously sourced ingredients from around the world in a blend of woody and floral notes.

name: Gucci
description: Gucci by Gucci Eau de Parfum by Gucci is a Chypre Floral fragrance for women. Gucci by Gucci Eau de Parfum was launched in 2007.

name: FOGG
description: Fogg is a power packed deodorant that offers more than you bargain for. This perfumed body spray has an invigorating scent which envelops you in a pleasant smell for a long time.
